{"word":"G2820 - κληρόω - klēróō - klay-ro'-o - Obtain an inheritance","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κληρόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">klēróō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">klay-ro'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Obtain an inheritance</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுதந்தரமாகு"},{"paragraph":"to cast lots, determine by lot"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2819 - κλῆρος - klēros - klay'-ros/2819\">G2819</a>; to <i>allot</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>assign</i> (a privilege): - obtain an inheritance.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2624/2624\">G2624</a>, <a href=\"#/G2816/2816\">G2816</a>, <a href=\"#/G2817/2817\">G2817</a>, <a href=\"#/G2818/2818\">G2818</a>, <a href=\"#/G2819/2819\">G2819</a>, <a href=\"#/G2820/2820\">G2820</a>, <a href=\"#/G3647/3647\">G3647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3648/3648\">G3648</a>, <a href=\"#/G4345/4345\">G4345</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789/4789\">G4789</a>"}]}